bib_record.title: -UNTERSUCHUNG ANGEREGTER KERNZUSTANDE IN 68-ZN DURCH NEUTRONENEINFANG IN 67-ZN-

free_txt: .THE RESULTS OF SPECTRUM AND COINCIDENCE MEASUREMENTS
ARE ANALYSED TO GIVE AN EXTENDED TRANSITION
LEVELS. LEVEL POSITIONS,MULTIPOLE MIXING RATIOS AND
GAMMA BRANCHING RATIOS ARE DISCUSSED IN THE
FRAMEWORK OF VIBRATIONAL AND UNIFIED COLLECTIVE
TO AN INTENSITY OF 1000 FOR 1077.35 KEV GAMMA LINE.
TO AN INTENSITY OF 1000 FOR 6910.6 KEV LINE.
